{"tid":1083251,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實啲人改車改到咁撚嘈係咩心態？","createTime":"2019-03-29T13:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T14:39:53.000Z","uid":117460,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c1036b1775afe622c0544cb1e1b6651751db7aa4","tid":1083251,"uid":117460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T13:23:04.000Z","msg":"成日係街嘈住哂，係啊你引到我望你架車，但你架車又唔係型，聲就大，加速又唔見得快。<br />\n<br />\n每次呢啲特別嘈既車經過都只會覺得心情煩燥同覺得佢地好柒。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">究竟佢地係咩心態！？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">利申: 每日都有渣車，但無興趣將自己架車改到咁影響人。</span>"},{"pid":"9d178252b65a1260cee46748007b72eb53ab4426","tid":1083251,"uid":76747,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T13:24:27.000Z","msg":"快D,你唔識"},{"pid":"55e0c945498cc5e22ad1ebd5c29b8b87e6486571","tid":1083251,"uid":226216,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T13:24:37.000Z","msg":"你一望就輸咗啦"},{"pid":"a881d7f30161e06f73ee6b8d629350af9c13af74","tid":1083251,"uid":117460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55e0c945498cc5e22ad1ebd5c29b8b87e6486571","tid":1083251,"uid":226216,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T13:24:37.000Z","msg":"你一望就輸咗啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"但望完覺得佢柒，佢贏左啲咩😂"},{"pid":"7c410f6aa9a43f8b9bfe21488c2507adad9f557e","tid":1083251,"uid":226216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a881d7f30161e06f73ee6b8d629350af9c13af74","tid":1083251,"uid":117460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55e0c945498cc5e22ad1ebd5c29b8b87e6486571","tid":1083251,"uid":226216,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T13:24:37.000Z","msg":"你一望就輸咗啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"但望完覺得佢柒，佢贏左啲咩😂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T13:28:06.000Z","msg":"就係贏咗你望過去果一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed2a77e05afa0805c3979f92291ad9537ef34bf","tid":1